description:
En-Tan-Mo describes itself as a next-generation public chain project, which reportedly realizes SHD completeness. Based on the concepts of Nash equilibrium and value transfer, the core En-Tan-Mo team reportedly includes Prof. Thomas Sargent, winner of the 2011 Nobel Prize in Economics, Professor Sheldon Lee Glashow, a Nobel Prize-winning theoretical physicist, as well as scholars from California Institute of Technology.
